      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Cadmium in Cocoa: Understanding EU Limits and How to Comply</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        What every cocoa buyer needs to know about EU Regulation 2023/915, cadmium testing, and how to ensure your cocoa meets European standards.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-brand-300">
